title: Nekonaughey
description:
Already more than 130 thousand subscribers! Popular on Twitter manga about cat is now in the paper edition! 

Such a pathetic and why something cute. Unlucky cat "Nekonaughey" comes on stage! He tries, but nothing goes smoothly. However, a single day it does not stop your journey to success!

Meet the popular book about a cat with sympathy, smile and sorrow.
